></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rmp1665702598941.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rmp1665702598941.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rmp1665702598941.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rmp1665702598941\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $totocc\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rmp1665702598941___totocc_292879\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__topic_d90302e1_d90303e1_d90304e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__p_d90305e1_d90306e1_d90307e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__section_w1563ab1b7b5_w1564ab1b7_w1565ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__p_d90308e1_d90309e1_d90310e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">if ($totocc &gt; $totdbocc)</code> ...</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__topic_d60127e1_d60128e1_d60129e1_d60130e1_d60131e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1202372e84\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__d6157e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__topic_d60132e1_d60133e1_d60134e1_d60135e1_d60136e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1202372e138\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in $totocc</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__2\">\n Component is empty (1 empty occurrence in the component).\n <p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist or is not drawn on the component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__1\">\n &gt;1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9842e1_d9843e1_d9844e1__entry__2\">\n Number of occurrences in the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9845e1_d9846e1_d9847e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9845e1_d9846e1_d9847e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9845e1_d9846e1_d9847e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9845e1_d9846e1_d9847e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9845e1_d9846e1_d9847e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1102\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9845e1_d9846e1_d9847e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9845e1_d9846e1_d9847e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__topic_d60137e1_d60138e1_d60139e1_d60140e1_d60141e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1202372e260\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__topic_d60142e1_d60143e1_d60144e1_d60145e1_d60146e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1202372e269\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__p_d90326e1_d90327e1_d90328e1\">The following structure editor functions and statements affect the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__li_d35765e1_d35766e1_d35767e1\">^ADD_OCC adds 1 to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__li_d35768e1_d35769e1_d35770e1\">^INS_OCC adds 1 to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__li_d35771e1_d35772e1_d35773e1\">^REM_OCC subtracts 1 from <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__li_d35774e1_d35775e1_d35776e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">read</span> adds 1 to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__li_d35777e1_d35778e1_d35779e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">discard</span> reduces <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span> by the number of discarded occurrences.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__li_d35780e1_d35781e1_d35782e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span> sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span> to 1.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__p_d90329e1_d90330e1_d90331e1\">Activity on a component that displays a single occurrence of an entity affects the values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curhits</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__p_d90332e1_d90333e1_d90334e1\">For example, after the component is started, the user enters a retrieve profile which matches exactly ten occurrences in the database. ^NEXT_OCC is used to scan through each of the retrieved occurrences, perhaps making changes. After the last occurrence is reached, a new occurrence is added and all changed occurrences are stored.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__p_d90335e1_d90336e1_d90337e1\">The following table illustrates the differences between the values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curhits</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"5\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Sequence of Values for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>,\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curhits</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Activity\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curhits</span>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Form starts.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^RETRIEVE\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^NEXT_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^NEXT_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 3\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 3\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"5\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ...\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^NEXT_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 9\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 9\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^NEXT_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^NEXT_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"5\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4 rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Last occurrence message appears.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^ADD_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 11\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 10\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n ^STORE\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 11\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 11\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 11\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rmp1665702598941__table_d9848e1_d9849e1_d9850e1__entry__5\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 11\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__section_wfk_1lj_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1202372e607\">Example: Calculating Entered but Unstored Occurrences</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, the number of occurrences in the component\n               is compared with the number of occurrences in the database. If there are more\n               occurrences in the component, the ProcScript assumes that occurrences have been added\n               to the component structure. The number of database occurrences is subtracted from the\n               number of component occurrences, and the result is inserted into a message sent to\n               the user:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rmp1665702598941__pre_vbw_1lj_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail\nif ($totocc &gt; $totdbocc)\n $1 = ($totocc - $totdbocc)\n message \"%%$1 customer(s)%%% have been added\"\nendif\nend; detail</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmg1665702599090.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curhits</a><p>Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exa1665702598712.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curocc</a><p>Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgk1665702598390.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$hits</a><p>Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/beo1719857754417.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$totdbocc</a><p>Return the number of occurrences of the entity that have been retrieved from a database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531688\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531688\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$totocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $totocc Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component. $totocc { ( Entity ) } Example: if ($totocc > $totdbocc) ... Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $totocc Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 1 Component is empty (1 empty occurrence in the component). Entity does not exist or is not drawn on the component. >1 Number of occurrences in the component. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $totocc Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The following structure editor functions and statements affect the value of $totocc : ^ADD_OCC adds 1 to $totocc . ^INS_OCC adds 1 to $totocc . ^REM_OCC subtracts 1 from $totocc . read adds 1 to $totocc . discard reduces $totocc by the number of discarded occurrences. clear sets $totocc to 1. Activity on a component that displays a single occurrence of an entity affects the values returned by $totocc , $totdbocc , $curhits , and $hits . For example, after the component is started, the user enters a retrieve profile which matches exactly ten occurrences in the database. ^NEXT_OCC is used to scan through each of the retrieved occurrences, perhaps making changes. After the last occurrence is reached, a new occurrence is added and all changed occurrences are stored. The following table illustrates the differences between the values of $totocc , $totdbocc , $curhits , and $hits . Table 4. Sequence of Values for $totocc , $totdbocc , $curhits , and $hits Activity Value of $totocc Value of $totdbocc Value of $curhits Value of $hits Form starts. 1 0 0 0 ^RETRIEVE 1 1 -10 10 ^NEXT_OCC 2 2 -10 10 ^NEXT_OCC 3 3 -10 10 ... ^NEXT_OCC 9 9 -10 10 ^NEXT_OCC 10 10 -10 10 ^NEXT_OCC 10 10 10 10 Last occurrence message appears. ^ADD_OCC 11 10 10 10 ^STORE 11 11 11 11 Example: Calculating Entered but Unstored Occurrences In the following example, the number of occurrences in the component is compared with the number of occurrences in the database. If there are more occurrences in the component, the ProcScript assumes that occurrences have been added to the component structure. The number of database occurrences is subtracted from the number of component occurrences, and the result is inserted into a message sent to the user: trigger detail if ($totocc > $totdbocc) $1 = ($totocc - $totdbocc) message \"%%$1 customer(s)%%% have been added\" endif end; detail Copy Related Links $curhits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. $curocc Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist. $hits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. $totdbocc Return the number of occurrences of the entity that have been retrieved from a database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}